                            <li>     Two sets of lease terms to be initialed by the 'Manager in Charge' and stamped on all pages.</li>
                            <li>     Copy of valid insurance policies: third party liability, all risks insurance and workers compensation (as per lease terms).  <a href="{!URLFOR($Resource.InsuranceForms)}">Click here to download Insurance form</a> </li>
                            <li>     Cheques (PDC) are to be prepared as per payment schedule in the lease details.</li>
                            <li>     All cheque payments to be addressed to <b style="color: #37494A;">TECOM Investments FZ-LLC</b>.</li>
                            <li>     In case cheques are not from  COMPANY NAME (such as personal cheques / different company) then an undertaking must be submitted by the issuer on behalf of the tenant along with the cheques.<a href="{!URLFOR($Resource.Undertakingpayement)}">Click here to download Undertaking Doc</a></li>
                            <li>     Ejari Fee <b style="color: #37494A;">AED 204.00</b> is applicable per lease and can be included along with the First payment. Ejari is payable only on lease agreements.</li> 
                            <li>     EMPOST will collect documents and cheque  from Sunday to Thursday  between 9am to 4pm .</li>
                            <li>     The signed lease document and receipts will be delivered once it has been counter signed by TECOM.</li> 
                            <li>     For any clarification, please contact axs call center: <b style="color: #37494A;">800 4297</b>.</li> <br/><br/>
                        </ul>

                        </div>  
                        </apex:outputPanel> 
                    
                    <apex:pageBlockSection collapsible="false" columns="1" id="pbBkof" rendered="{!if((((rq.STA__c=='Draft' || rq.STA__c == 'Open') && (md.isNew)) || md.isEdit),true,false)}" title="Select Agreement(s)" > 
